snippet.title: ★v4.9 [Outworld Traveler] Trailer★ - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
The Honkai Impact 3rd × Genshin Impact crossover version, v4.9 [Outworld Traveler], is close to launch! SP battlesuit [Prinzessin der Verurteilung!] debuts!
Crossover event [Outworld Quest], new equipment [Mitternachts Waltz] and Moonwatcher set... More to come!

Subscribe our YouTube and turn on notification for latest video : http://bit.ly/HonkaiImpact3rdYTB
